description:
Quizmine and RealSimpleEDU.com brings you "On-The-Go" learning and reference for Algebra II


App is continuously updated based on your feedback.


App offers 20 interactive tutorials and 5 quizzes with search feature.


Includes following tutorials:


Polynomial Basics,

Polynomial Division,

Synthetic Division,

Factoring Polynomials,

Linear Algebra,

Matrix Applications,

Linear Inequalities,

Linear Equations and Functions,

Linear Inequalities and Graphs,

Logarithms,

Absolute Value,

Sequences and Series,

Counting,

Probability,

Complex Numbers,

Conic Sections,

Circle and Parabola,

Ellipse and Hyperbola,

Quadratic Equations,

Formula Pack.


Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.


Our Mission: A Quizmine & RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.


Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
